{"tid":1439683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下一波運動要點 要文宣","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:48:36.000Z","uid":289157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d94609cc8678a1b14e2507d8c9c1bc05172bccac","tid":1439683,"uid":289157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:41:29.000Z","msg":"既然林病咁著眼係經濟 因為香港沉默大多數最著眼點係經濟 所以林病先打住經濟牌 林病仲痴心地覺得沉默既大多數係唔會想佢落台<br />\n所以下一波行動必然係令沉默既大多數都反佢<br />\n所以我地要搞不問價全城齊沽樓 沽到跌三成係起碼<br />\n文宣方向可以係年輕人可以連命都唔要 言輩要做反d野 不問價齊沽樓 唔係咁簡單為香港做少少野都唔得"},{"pid":"5e4a3a05789123e26f50a0d2afdd554368815cf6","tid":1439683,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"大埔@1542 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=49c6d138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uigjSQB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuigjSQB.png&h=7d8a578d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"}]}